summary:
Enthusiastic Software Engineer, Software Development is not only job to me, its my interest.

More than 4 years experience in Software Development.

Very passionate about programming competitions. Try to regularly participate in online programming competitions. Also interested in problem setting and created many problems for national level programming competitions in Bangladesh.
